enb_long_title: Twenty-sixth sessions of the Subsidiary Bodies (SB 26) of the United Nations Framework Convention on Climate Change (UNFCCC)
sentences: The Secretariat introduced the item on demonstrable progress on commitments under the Protocol (Article 3.2), and documents synthesizing reports from parties ( FCCC/SBI/2006/INF.2 and INF.4 ).
Informal consultations will be conducted by Henrià tte Bersee (Netherlands) and Arthur Rolle (Bahamas).
